    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty car, and it's been such a joy to drive. It's in really solid shape and has been super dependable for me\u2014perfect for someone who wants a great ride that's been well-cared for. It runs smoothly and still looks fantastic on the road. I'd love for it to go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have. Come by and take it for a test drive!",
