    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies. This example is tailored for the driver, equipped with a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural integrity under lateral load. The suspension geometry is preserved with refreshed bushings and Bilstein B6 dampers, providing excellent damping frequency and road feedback. The engine maintains strong compression and pulls cleanly to the 8,000 RPM redline. While the aesthetic condition shows honest patina consistent with spirited use, the drivetrain and chassis remain tight and track-ready.",
      "price": 31500.0,
