      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a gem. It\u2019s in great shape and has been super well-maintained, so it\u2019s totally ready to hit the road with a new owner! It drives smoothly, looks wonderful, and has plenty of life left for all your upcoming adventures. I've really loved driving this car, and I'm sure you will too. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 34500.0,
